org.apache.james.protocols.api

Interface StartTlsResponse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Response
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FutureStartTlsResponse, POP3StartTlsResponse, SMTPStartTlsResponse

    public interface StartTlsResponse
extends Response
    An special sub-type of Response which makes it possible to detect a response to a STARTTLS request. After writing this response its a MUST to enable STARTTLS before further processing
